Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:37.10,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几十亿年如一日\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I'm talking for billions of years.
