Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.21,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}易如反掌个鬼啊\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Duck soup, my ass.
