Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:22.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彼得森意识到他必须用酸来煮容器和工具\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Patterson realized he would have to boil his containers and tools in acid
