Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.58,0:32:49.48,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对含铅汽油做出讨伐\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that would make the case against leaded gasoline.
