Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.69,0:33:15.16,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反击开始了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the push-back began.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.65,0:33:27.15,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-你好 彼得森博士 -很高兴见到你\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Hello, Dr. Patterson. - Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.18,0:33:28.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您的研究成果很了不起\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Very impressed by your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.78,0:33:34.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您的研究成果对我们石油化工行业有很大的影响\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Your work is of great interest to us in the petroleum and chemical industries
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.69,0:33:37.82,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多亏了你们的赞助\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, it wouldn't have been possible without your funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.86,0:33:41.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 我们还希望提供给你更多的帮助\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Precisely. And there's so much more we'd like to do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.86,0:33:45.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正好 我还想在极地冰层中测量铅含量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I've been thinking about measuring lead in polar ice
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.86,0:33:49.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看看是不是和海洋中的结果一样\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to see if it shows the same kind of pattern as the oceans.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.36,0:33:52.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}铅 你的工作已经结束了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Lead? But you've already done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.03,0:33:56.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是时候研究其它微量元素了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're thinking it's time you move on to other trace elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.03,0:33:58.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实 彼得森博士\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In fact, Dr. Patterson,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.37,0:34:04.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们有能力资助你去无限制地研究其它方面\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}our ability to fund you in any other line of research is...Virtually limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.31,0:34:08.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}铅是一种神经毒素\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Lead is a neurotoxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.04,0:34:11.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们将四乙基铅从工厂运出来时\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When you ship your tetraethyl lead from the factory...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.78,0:34:13.64,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在加进汽油之前\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before you add it to the gasoline...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.68,0:34:15.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像是运送化学武器\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's handled just like a chemical weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.68,0:34:17.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是有原因的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's a reason for that.
