Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.27,0:34:29.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}基欧博士已经证明了这种程度的铅\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dr. Kehoe has shown that the level of lead in the environment
