Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.96,0:34:37.66,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那它怎么会在深层海水中存在呢\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then why doesn't it show up in the deep water? Here,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.69,0:34:39.96,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我给你看\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}let me just show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.99,0:34:42.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多谢了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thanks for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.46,0:34:47.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 你们还要把上百万吨的毒气排到我们呼吸的空气中吗\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wait, you're just gonna keep on putting millions of tons of poison into the air we breathe?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.36,0:34:52.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算我的研究不能使你们停产 以后也有科学家可以做到\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If my research doesn't put you out of business some future scientist will
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.40,0:34:56.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}石油行业来的赞助一夜之间消失得无影无踪\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Patterson's funding from the oil industry vanished overnight
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.54,0:34:59.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事实上 他们要让他失业\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In fact, they tried to get him fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.54,0:35:03.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是美国政府 陆军 海军\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the U.S. government... The Army, the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.01,0:35:07.48,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原子能委员会 公共卫生署\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the atomic energy commission, the public health service,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.51,0:35:10.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有国家科学基金会 都支持他\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the National Science Foundation... Stood by him,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.71,0:35:13.18,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}支持他的铅污染研究\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}supporting his research on lead pollution.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.21,0:35:19.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了调查研究 从最北的格陵兰到最南的大西洋都有他的足迹\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}His investigations took him from Greenland in the far north to Antarctica in the far south
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.35,0:35:23.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}足迹遍布各个河流与山川\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and to rivers, mountains and valleys in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.89,0:35:27.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使面对最恶劣的条件\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In even the most hostile conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.92,0:35:30.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彼得森和他的团队协力复制了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Patterson and his team worked to replicate
