Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.33,0:35:36.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们每天都更换塑料制服\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Their plastic suits were replaced daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.16,0:35:39.96,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在零下温度下中工作10-12个小时\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Working ten-to 12-hour days in subzero weather,
