Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.00,0:35:44.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}约为61米
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.70,0:35:46.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是某种程度上的时间旅行\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was a form of time travel,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.70,0:35:49.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}取得了那是在工业革命开始前\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to recover snow that had fallen three centuries ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.90,0:35:53.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}300年前的雪样\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before the start of the Industrial Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.07,0:35:55.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的鼻子\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.87,0:35:57.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快擦鼻子\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wipe your nose, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.01,0:36:01.47,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你体内的铅比冰里的高1千倍\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's a thousand times more lead in you than in this ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.54,0:36:04.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这是想要污染整个样本吗\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You want to contaminate the whole damn sample?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.21,0:36:13.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}经过4个星期的精疲力尽的艰苦样本采集工作后\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}After four grueling weeks of painstaking sample collection
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.12,0:36:16.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彼得森准备回到实验室了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Patterson was ready to go back to the lab.
