Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.42,0:36:27.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不论在地球上的其它什么地方\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No matter where he searched on earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.72,0:36:30.52,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不管多久以前的样本\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}no matter how far he traveled back in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.56,0:36:33.49,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果都说明一件事\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the results always told the same story:
