Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.60,0:36:46.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几千年来 人们都知道\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For thousands of years, lead had been known
