Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.57,0:36:53.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暴力行为 甚至致命\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}violent behavior, and even death.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.11,0:36:55.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在地球年龄的研究中\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In searching for the age of the earth,
