Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.02,0:37:08.72,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是基欧和其它受雇于铅工业的科学家\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But Kehoe and the other scientists employed by the lead industry
