Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.10,0:37:39.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}包括一位很有影响力的参议员\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}including one highly influential senator.
